values: "With sculptural depictions rich in realism reflecting the turbulent era of samurai. These 13th-century masterpieces offer a unique glimpse into a time of strife, captured through the serene yet vivid artistry of Kaikei."

"Tako Tora serves up Takoyaki that's hard to resist. With its crispy exterior, gooey center, and delicious sauce, it's a must-try for both dine-in and takeaway experiences."

A local favorite near Kitano-tenmangu Shrine
